JAAS authentication example, uses code from:
JAAS Authentication Tutorial
https://docs.oracle.com/javase/7/docs/technotes/guides/security/jaas/tutorials/GeneralAcnOnly.html

JAAS Authorization is not considered here, as deprecated option.
